#. §1: `exact e`
#. §2: `e`
#. §3: `⊢ P₁ ∧ P₂ ∧ P₃ ∧ P₄`
#. §4: `constructor`
#. §5: ```
#. refine ⟨?_,?_,?_,?_⟩
#. ```
#. §6: `h : P₃`
#. §7: ```
